OL,3,CKiller of Claire Knights has jail
OL,4,Csentence increased by Court of Appeal
OL,6,FA pub chef who murdered a woman while
OL,7,Fshe walked her dog will spend nearly
OL,8,Fsix more years in prison after Court
OL,9,Fof Appeal judges increased his
OL,10,Fsentence.
OL,12,FHarrison Lawrence Van-Pooss was jailed
OL,13,Ffor life with a minimum term of 25-and-
OL,14,Fa-half years in February for killing
OL,15,FClaire Knights, 54, in Kent almost two
OL,16,Fyears ago.
OL,18,FHe ambushed her as she walked back
OL,19,Ffrom a beach near Minnis Bay, sexually
OL,20,Fassaulted and then murdered her before
OL,21,Fhiding her body in a dyke.
