OL,6,FThe 21-year-old then "feigned"
OL,7,Fsymptoms of psychosis following his
OL,8,Farrest, the Court of Appeal was told
OL,9,Fon Friday.
OL,11,FHis sentence was referred by the
OL,12,FSolicitor General for being unduly
OL,13,Flenient, with Lord Justice Edis, Mr
OL,14,FJustice Calver and Judge Angela Morris
OL,15,Fincreasing Van-Pooss' minimum term to
OL,16,Fone of 31 years
