OL,3,CKiller of Claire Knights has jail
OL,4,Csentence increased by Court of Appeal
OL,6,FJonathan Polnay KC, for the SG, said
OL,7,Fthe judge at Canterbury Crown Court
OL,8,Fdid not give enough weight to how Ms
OL,9,FKnights had been targeted as a lone
OL,10,Fwoman, the extreme nature of the
OL,11,Fviolence and that her body had been
OL,12,Fhidden for two days before it was
OL,13,Fdiscovered.
OL,15,FHe also said the judge gave too much
OL,16,Fcredit for Van-Pooss's guilty plea and
OL,17,Fhis sentence therefore "required an
OL,18,Fuplift of substance".
