OL,6,FHe then built a "den" by the railway
OL,7,Flines near Minnis Bay, Lord Justice
OL,8,FEdis said in his judgment.
OL,10,FMs Knights was believed to have been
OL,11,Fwalking a white and brown spaniel
OL,12,Fcalled Zebulon when she ran into Van-
OL,13,FPooss the following day.
OL,15,FVan-Pooss acted in a "simple" and
OL,16,F"calculated" way, the judge added, as
OL,17,Fhe beat her and stomped on her head,
OL,18,Fcausing fractures and brain damage.
