OL,6,FMs Knights was found concealed in a
OL,7,Fdyke, having been pushed into the
OL,8,Fwater while she was still alive.
OL,10,FVan-Pooss was arrested for the
OL,11,Fupskirting offence on the evening of
OL,12,Fthe killing, and was later charged
OL,13,Fwith murder.
OL,15,FLord Justice Edis said the killing of
OL,16,Fa lone woman created "widespread
OL,17,Fconcern in the local community" and
OL,18,Fthat Van-Pooss received an unduly
OL,19,Flenient sentence.
