OL,6,FHe said: "We consider that the judge,
OL,7,Fin approaching this difficult task,
OL,8,Fdid fall into error because even
OL,9,Fhaving regard to double counting, the
OL,10,Faggravating factors did outweigh the
OL,11,Fmitigating factors."
OL,13,FSolicitor General Lucy Rigby said:
OL,14,F"Lawrence Van-Pooss's attack on Claire
OL,15,FKnights was horrific. He assaulted and
OL,16,Fbrutally murdered her, in a totally
OL,17,Frandom attack.
